v2.21 [august 2005]
- added option not to strip filename extensions
- removed "system" commands in configure
- removed all relative directory addressing in favour of FindBins


v2.2 [february 2005]
- support for paths in identifiers
- support for retaining original identifiers
- faster engine to process requests
- support for large file sets
- optional multiple-set membership
- optional list size calculation
- support for set descriptions
- fixed OAI compliance problems


v2.1 [december 2002]
- fixed junk set names error
- support for set name mappings


v2.0 [july 2002]
- support for OAI-PMH2
- better and more general configuration


v1.0 [october 2001]
- first release
